//+------------------------------------------------------------------+
//| Basic constrained test: nonsmooth Rosenbrock posed as box        |
//| constrained problem.                                             |
//|            [                         ]                           |
//|   minimize [ 10*|x0^2-x1| + (1-x0)^2 ]                           |
//|            [                         ]                           |
//| s.t. x0<=1/sqrt(2), x1<=0.5                                      |
//| It's exact solution is x0=1/sqrt(2), x1=1/2                      |
